TaskTimer — Custom Favicon Folder
==================================

Place your custom favicon here:

  favicon.png  — Browser tab icon (recommended: 512x512 PNG)

The server will automatically serve this file at /favicon.png.
If no file is present, the browser shows its default icon.

How to use:
  1. Create or export a PNG icon (512x512 recommended)
  2. Name it exactly: favicon.png
  3. Copy it into this folder (backend/public/icons/)
  4. Restart the server — the new icon appears in the browser tab

Free tool to create a PNG favicon:
  https://favicon.io/favicon-generator/
